### External API Smoke Tests

# Set your base URL and API key
@base = http://localhost:2053
@key = TEST_EXTERNAL_KEY

### No key -> expect 401
GET {{base}}/api/external/server/status

### Wrong key -> expect 401
GET {{base}}/api/external/server/status
X-API-Key: WRONG

### Correct key -> expect 200 JSON
GET {{base}}/api/external/server/status
X-API-Key: {{key}}

### Inbounds list -> expect 200 JSON
GET {{base}}/api/external/inbounds/list
X-API-Key: {{key}}
